snippet.title: Foxtrot: New FPS multiplayer action × Foxtrot announcement gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Foxtrot is a new multiplayer FPS action game. Join class-based matches on various maps in Foxtrot Open Beta coming 19. May 2021.

KNOW MORE ABOUT FOXTROT
Official site https://foxtrotgame.gq
Twitter: https://twitter.com/foxtrotgame
Play game for free: https://wisegames.itch.io/foxtrot
Read more about Foxtrot below in the video's description.

WISE GAMES INTERACTIVE
Official site: https://wisegames.gq
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WiseGames1
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wisegames

MAY CONTAIN CONTENT INAPPROPRIATE FOR CHILDREN
The game was not rated yet. Read more about children safety at https://pegi.info



Foxtrot is a new multiplayer FPS experience. Pick a team and join the battle - only the best wins. Foxtrot has four classes - Assault, Engineer, Recon, or Heavy. Who do you prefer?

Assault - Rush into enemy line and kill 'em all
Engineer - Shotgun master
Recon - Just a sniper
Heavy - Man with a semi-automatic grenade launcher
You can edit loadout of each class. 

We have multiple game modes in Foxtrot.
Free for all
Team deathmatch
Capture the flag
Cover point
Gun rush
